[I] Python package and dependency manager supporting the latest PEP standards

[T] Modern Python package and dependency manager supporting the latest PEP standards,
[T] such as PEP 517 and PEP 621. Provides a simple and fast dependency resolver and
[T] flexible plugin-in system. It supports management of virtual environments (venvs) in
[T] both project and centralized locations, similar to Pipevn. Unlike Poetry and Hatch,
[T] users can specify the build backend they prefer.

[U] https://pdm-project.org/

[A] Frost Ming <mianghong@gmail.com>
[M] Paul Manners <paul.manners@yahoo.com>

[C] extra/tool
